quran[26]{c,v,t}:
  42,51,"Soni nganiyiŵa kwa mundu yanti ni kum’bechetekasya jwalakwejo Allah, ikaŵeje ni maloŵe gakuuwulidwa (mu ntima mwakwe), kapena kusyeto kwa chakusiŵilila (gambaga kupikana maloŵe ga Allah mwangali kum’bona), kapena kuntumisya Ntenga (Jibulilu) basi ni kun’juwulila yaakuisaka (Allah) kwa lisosa Lyakwe. Chisimu Jwalakwe ni Jwapenani kusyene, Jwalunda lwakusokoka"
  42,52,Iyyoyopeyo soni tun’juwulile mmwe (Muhammadi ﷺ) maloŵe (Qur’an) kwa ulamusi Wetu. Nganimmanyililaga kuti Chitabu ni chichi namuno chikulupi. Nambo tujitesile jalakwe (Qur’an) kuŵa lilanguka lyatukun’jongolela nalyo jwatukunsaka mwa achikapolo Ŵetu. Soni chisimu mmwe (Muhammadi ﷺ) nkongolelaga kwene kwitala lyagoloka
  42,53,Litala lya Allah Ajula jwaili Yakwe (Jikape yosope) yaili kumawunde ni yaili petaka. Manyililani yanti kwa Allah ikuujila ichindu yosope
  43,1,Hâ. Mîm
  43,2,Nguchilumbila Chitabu (cha Qur’an) chakusalichisya
  43,3,Chisimu Uwwe tujitesile jalakweji kuŵa Qur’an jacharabu kuti jenumanja mpate kugataga mu lunda (mate gakwe chenene)
  43,4,"Soni chisimu jalakwe (Qur’an) m’Mama jwa chitabu (Al-Lauh Al-Mahfȗz) jwali Kukwetu jili japenani kusyene, jegumbale lunda lwakusokoka"
  43,5,Ana tuntyochesye ŵanganyammwe chikumbusyo (Qur’an) kutyosya kwene (kwakuleka kunnamula ni kunkanya najo) ligongo lyanti n’di ŵakusumba mpika (pa ungalumbana)
  43,6,Ana Achimitume ŵalingwa ŵatwatumiisye mu (ŵandu) ŵandanda
  43,7,Soni nganiŵaichililaga ntume jwalijose ikaŵeje ŵaliji nkuntenda chipongwe
  43,8,"Basi ni twajonasile (ŵandu ŵakala) ŵakupelenganya nnope machili kwapunda ŵanganyao (Makuraishi), ni ipite ilandanyo ya (ŵandu) ŵandanda (yaŵatite kapedwe ilagasyo nambo Makuraishi ngagakukulupilila)"
  43,9,"Soni naga n’di mwawusyisye kuti: “Ana nduni juŵagumbile mawunde ni mataka?” Chisimu tajile: “Jwagagumbile (Allah) Jwamachili gakupunda, Jwakumanyilila nnope.”"
  43,10,"Ajula jwantendele litaka kuŵa chakutandika, ni am’bichile palakwepo matala kuti jenumanja n’dijongolele kwakuja"
  43,11,"Ni Ajula jwaatulwisye kuumila kwinani mesi mwan’dingo (wakuŵajilwa), basi ni tujimwisye nago chilambo chachiwe, iyyoyopeyo soni tinchikoposyedwa (m’malembe)"
  43,12,"Ni Ajula jwaagumbile chachilume ni chachikongwe mu ichindu yosope, ni am’bichile yombo ni ilango yankuikwela"
  43,13,"Kuti ntamilichicheje pa migongo pakwe, kaneka ni nkumbuchileje chindimba cha M’mbuje gwenu (Allah) pati ntamilichiche pachanya pakwepo, ni kuŵechetaga kuti: “Kuswejela ni Kwakwe Ajula (Allah) jwaatujepepachisye achi, soni uwwe nga nganitukombola kulumbikana nacho (mwamachili getu).”"
  43,14,“Soni chisimu uwwe kwa Ambuje ŵetu (Allah) chituwujile kwene.”
  43,15,"Ni am’bichile (Allah) mwa achikapolo Ŵakwe chipande (pakuŵecheta kuti: Achimalaika ŵanache ŵa Allah). Chisimu mundu ni mmakaani jwakuonechela"
  43,16,"Kapena (Allah) alitendele ŵanache ŵachikongwe mu yaagumbile, sano jenumanja ni ansagulile ŵanache ŵachilume"
  43,17,"Soni naga jumo jwao juli jupedwile abali ja ayila yannandanyichisye (Allah) Jwaukoto wejinji (yakola mwanache jwankongwe), basi ngope jakwe jikasapiilila, soni gakasan’gumbala madandausi"
  43,18,"Ha! Ana jwaaleledwe mu ipeto, soni jwalakwe pa ukangani nganijuŵa juŵechete mwakupikanika (ni jwankumpa Allah, ŵali ŵanache ŵachikongwe)"
  43,19,"Ni agatesile Malaika gagali achikapolo ŵa (Allah) Jwaukoto wejinji kuŵa achakongwe. Ana ŵakuweni gumbidwa kwao? Umboni wao tiulembedwe, ni tachiwusyidwa"
  43,20,"Ni akutiji: “(Allah) Jwaukoto wejinji angasache (kuti tukagalagatila isanamu) nga nganituigalagatila.” Nganakola ŵanganyao umanyilisi uliose pa yele (yaakuŵechetayo), nganaŵa ŵanganyao ikaŵeje agamba kusepelela unami basi"
  43,21,"Kapena twapele ŵanganyao chitabu nkanichiŵe achi (cha Qur’an), sano ŵanganyao ni akulikamulichisya mu chalakwecho (akuipata mwalakwemo yaakuŵechetayo)"
  43,22,"(Ngwamba), nambo akutiji: “Chisimu uwwe twasimene achatati ŵetu ali pa nyendele ja dini (jagalagatila isanamu), sano uwwe nowe tukulondola sajo syao.”"
  43,23,"Soni iyyoyopeyo nganitutumisyeje paujo penu (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ) m’musi uliose nkutetela jwalijose, ikaŵeje ŵaŵechetaga ŵakulipatila ŵao kuti: “Chisimu uwwe twasimene achatati ŵetu ali pa nyendele ja dini (jagalagatila isanamu), sano uwwe nowe tukuya sajo syao.”"